N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 19 ยง 1107.23 - Advertisements

State Regulations

An educational institution or other organization offering
approved courses may not make or publish a false or misleading statement
regarding employment opportunities which may be available as the result of the
successful completion of a course of study, or upon acquisition of a
license. Notes
